    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>mayo </strong>to a bowl with the <strong>remaining grated</strong> <strong>garlic </strong>(not a fan of raw garlic? Just add a little!), 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and mix together – this is your <strong>garlic mayo</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper and shred finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>finely</p>",
