      "instruction": "<p>Once the chips are done, push them to one side and add your <strong>wholemeal pitta[s] </strong>to the other side of the tray[s]</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for a final 2-3 min or until the pitta[s] is warmed through</p>",
