      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>warmed</strong> <strong>pitta</strong> in half and fill with the <strong>cooked chicken</strong>,<strong> quick-pickled onion salad </strong>and some of the <strong>garlic mayo </strong>– this is your <strong>chicken thigh shawarma pitta</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chicken thigh shawarma pitta</strong> with the <strong>chips,</strong> <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>quick-pickled onion salad </strong>and<strong> garlic mayo </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
